caption.title: Histogram of the number of peaks found in the infection time course over 1000 runs of the case of strong population immune strength.
caption.p: The parameters are those used in Fig 4. Peaks were found using FindPeaks, a Mathematica utility, after being smoothed by Wiener filtering. More than half the samples in this strongly immune case have only one peak in contrast to the weakly immune case in S2 Fig.
